TransDub Studio
================

TransDub Studio is a modified downstream build based on pyVideoTrans:

    https://github.com/jianchang512/pyvideotrans

The original pyVideoTrans project is licensed under the GNU General Public
License version 3.0 (GPL-3.0). This modified version is distributed under the
same license.

This repository is not the official pyVideoTrans project. Changes in this
downstream build include local macOS app/deployment improvements, DeepSeek
context-translation tuning, and F5-TTS dubbing reliability fixes.

The original authors retain copyright over their original work. Downstream
modifications are provided under GPL-3.0 as part of this modified version.
